## Future Patterns

The following patterns are possible with SOE but not yet documented:

### Fractal Orchestration
Child workflows spawning child workflows, ad infinitum. A "CEO" workflow spawns "Manager" workflows, which spawn "Worker" workflows.

### Universal Backend
Any workflow can be wrapped as a tool for another workflow. A "Research Agent" workflow becomes a tool for a "Writer Agent" workflow.

### Edge AI
SOE has no heavy dependencies. It can run on Raspberry Pi with local LLMs (Llama.cpp), or in the browser via WebAssembly.

